  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A translucent barrier of magical force originates from you and protects you along with a number of creatures equal to your creatures spellcasting modifier that you can see of your choice within a 15-foot-radius of you.</p><p>Each creature within the barrier shares the highest AC and the shares the highest result of any saving throw. Additionally, any sources of damage reduction, resistance and immunity are also shared by creatures within the barrier.</p><p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 4th level or higher, the barrier radius is increased by 5 feet for each slot level above 3rd.</p><p>If cast with a spell slot of 9th level or higher, the radius is 120 feet and has not limit to the number of creatures that can be protected by the barrier.</p>",
